---
// Features Component
---
<!-- Why Choose AmerisPro -->
    <section id="features" class="reveal" style="background: white; border-top: 2.5px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--border); max-width: 100%;">
        <div style="max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px;">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Designed for High-Compliance Sites</h2>
                <p>A reliable architecture built to assist safety officers and protect industrial work zones.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid stagger-children">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon-box">🔒</div>
                    <h4>Private Cloud DB</h4>
                    <p>Connects directly to your own Google Drive. No external database servers or recurring server costs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon-box">⚡</div>
                    <h4>Lightweight & Fast</h4>
                    <p>Designed with clean clientside scripts and responsive CSS frameworks. Responsive on mobile and tablet devices.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon-box">📋</div>
                    <h4>Ready for Audits</h4>
                    <p>Instant detailed review popup, signature stamp logs, and PDF printing to quickly verify safety checks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>